<%= @account.full_name %>,

<% if @admin -%>
Hello! <%= @admin.full_name %> has added you to <%= @organization.name %>'s sourceAFRICA account.
<% else -%>
Hello! A sourceAFRICA account has been created for you and <%= @organization.name %>.
<% end -%>

Set your password and get started at:
<%= DC.server_root(:force_ssl => true) %>/accounts/enable/<%= @account.security_key.key %>

Once you've set your password, you can login at <%= DC.server_root %>/login using <%= @account.email %> as your username. Information about using the workspace, creating accounts, searching the repository and more is available on the help tab.

